      <elementaryExchange id="52c6814b-5b0b-503a-adcb-39e382057ab8" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7" casNumber="000075-21-8" amount="0.003833" elementaryExchangeId="17bd5f8c-bd48-4cfc-80c0-1aa251f4bf43" formula="C2H4O">
        <name xml:lang="en">Ethylene oxide</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">The remaining amount of unreacted ethylene oxide is assumed to leave the production process with the waste water. Further it was assumed that this wastewater is treated in a internal wastewater plant. The removal efficiency for ethylene oxide is assumed with 90%. The carbon contained in the removed ethylene oxide is accounted as CO2 emissions to air.</comment>
